{"title":"锦绣淮南","authors":["邹荻帆"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":6,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦绣淮南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邹荻帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马奔腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上白云飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上麦穗醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马奔腾追风蹄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员开起比学赶帮会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红透的思想饱满的穗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风帆齐发下淮河；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎头追上不算晚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志同道合理应当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一队组织儿童护幼林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一队老人报名拾肥粪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一队玉米田里点豇豆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一队黄豆地里花生稠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要见缝插针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路边坡旁点豆瓜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不临渴掘井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开垦荒地种桑麻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茬口安排好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织锦缎上绣鲜花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳力调派对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连锁的原子在爆炸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一队耕读学校学农艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样板田里试技术；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一队学习小组讲理论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张弓搭箭射目的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴水利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕子来时绿水人家绕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办交通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运肥车通过了石板桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈养猪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥猪头头是百宝箱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说放羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊毛出在羊身上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一千个心窍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都用在比学赶帮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一万种智慧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要建设革命化的家乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动比学赶帮的长鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾驭多快好省的骏马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓足自力更生的干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的斗志风发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上白云飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上麦穗醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马奔腾乘东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员开起比学赶帮会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地上作文章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在淠史杭灌渠堤坝上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着滚滚翻腾的麦浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说这是春潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在东风里猛涨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是社会主义的思潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在淮南平原上激荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是思想的力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成了春潮汪洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必说大雁来时抢种忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必说积肥时惊起野鸭渡寒塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今春风送绿归杨柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们在大地上作文章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们来除草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩草除根保苗秧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们去浇水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给株株麦苗送乳浆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集中兵力歼灭红蜘蛛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷雾器不够又何妨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长袜筒里藏杀虫粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象当年用土地雷杀匪帮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当城市运来了肥田粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塑料袋象天鹅在碧波中游航，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们撒播化肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象白李花在春水上飘香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是锦绣河山的好文章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汹涌着春潮般的力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看桃杏在田野上用朱笔圈点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能不把这诗篇百倍欣赏。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}